---
import StarlightPage from "@astrojs/starlight/components/StarlightPage.astro";
---

<StarlightPage
  frontmatter={{
    title: "Privacy Policy",
    description: "Privacy Policy for the Demo Time for PowerPoint addin",
    tableOfContents: false,
  }}
>
  <div class="privacy-page">
    <header class="hero">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>
        Your privacy is important to us. This policy outlines how we collect,
        use, and protect your information when using the Demo Time for
        PowerPoint addin.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="privacy-section">
      <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        The Demo Time for PowerPoint addin does not collect any personal or
        usage information.
      </p>

      <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>
        As the addin does not collect any information, there is no data to use
        or share.
      </p>

      <h2>3. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        Since no data is collected, there is no data to secure. The addin
        operates entirely locally on your device.
      </p>

      <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        You have the assurance that the Demo Time for PowerPoint addin respects
        your privacy by not collecting any information.
      </p>

      <h2>5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to update this privacy policy at any time. Changes
        will be posted on this page, and continued use of the addin constitutes
        acceptance of the updated policy.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please
        contact us at elio@struyfconsulting.be.
      </p>

      <p>Thank you for trusting Demo Time for PowerPoint!</p>
    </section>
  </div>
</StarlightPage>
